<task id="task_715972DECF1246A0A3B67800293FBD25">
  <title>Annotate a card</title>
  <shortdesc>Annotate a card. Other users with whom you have shared the board
	 can view the annotation and add annotations. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Marketing Cloud" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_3733DF5C92584DF7A94332D37B908DD8">
      <step id="step_B9A0D58178EC40F68BF21C299E062B31">
        <cmd> In the left navigation menu, click 
			 <uicontrol>Feed</uicontrol>, then click the desired card to open it. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
      <step id="step_1B228865D8664940B3F5FFDF436445A3">
        <cmd>Click 
			 <uicontrol>Draw Annotation</uicontrol>. 
		  </cmd>
        <info>
          <p>
            <image href="graphics/card_draw.png" id="image_AFA0EDEB7EDF4268889FD170A235BC53">
              <?xm-replace_text Paragraph?>
            </image>
          </p>
        </info>
      </step>
      <step id="step_4D115BD421E744D4A8E53B362C3038EE">
        <cmd>Use your mouse on a computer or your finger on a tablet to draw an
			 arrow or a circle on the card to highlight the desired element. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
</task>